{"id":612945,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/06/【立此存照】网友吐槽中国电费贵-国资委回应：建/","date":"2019-06-27T14:19:59Z","modified":"2019-06-27T14:19:59Z","title":"【立此存照】网友吐槽中国电费贵 国资委回应：建议移民","content":"<p>@法制日报：【#网友吐槽中国电费贵#国资委硬核配图怼：建议移民】26日，国资委官微@国资小新 发布了一段白鹤滩水电站建造历程的视频，介绍这个全球在建规模最大的水电站。 但有位网友评论吐槽中国电费贵，国资委回复“建议移民”，其他官微纷纷转发。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-612947\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie4v-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"531\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie4v-1.jpg 745w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie4v-1-300x290.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p>在受到广泛质疑后，@国资小新 重新修改了该条回复，并且更新了一篇文章<a href=\"https://weibo.com/ttarticle/p/show?id=2309404387744653665528\">《中国的电价比西方发达国家高吗？真相是…》</a>文章仅从电价绝对值比较，得出中国电价低于各国电价的结论。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-612948\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie42.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"549\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie42.jpg 740w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie42-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie42-300x300.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie42-70x70.jpg 70w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/D-DqY2CU4AAie42-50x50.jpg 50w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-612949\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/a40e3d09ly1g4ew3yo8rej20fa0rsdhr.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"1000\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/a40e3d09ly1g4ew3yo8rej20fa0rsdhr.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/06/a40e3d09ly1g4ew3yo8rej20fa0rsdhr-165x300.jpg 165w\" sizes=\"(max-wi